column5: Hello  I just received my personal best brown pic from a client.  It was taken last year November early morning and released to spawn away.....   Hope you enjoy  Dave
That's a beauty! I think that fish could eat my PB brown!
Geez, that thing is a monster.  My personal best from last year is alot uglier
WOW THAT LOOKS SCARY  Nice male screwed up face  Thanks  Dave
Dave, it was a nasty fish.  Any idea on what yours weighed?  Looked well into the teens.  Mine was ugly, but not that big, maybe around the 10lb mark or a bit less.

Nice fish Dave did you get it on one of the flies you gave me? Bill put the picture in a fire pit please lol a fish a will never forget   . If you ever wondered why I didnâ€™t want to eat that day look at the picture and you got your answer lol.
Now that's a brown! Great fish
Top fish mate, very nice Brown
thats a beauty for sure, oh gotta love those halloween browns with the messed up heads and teeth
wow that is ugly... the fish looks good though   just jokin!!
ive seen carp prettier than that thing lol
Dmasse, that fish is a beauty  Bill...that picture gives me nightmares
Beautiful massive brown Dave Congratulations Leechman
